<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب ش ع:</span> شَيْءٌ <span class="c2">(بَشِعٌ)</span> أَيْ كَرِيهُ الطَّعْمِ يَأْخُذُ بِالْحَلْقِ بَيِّنُ <span class="c2">(الْبَشَاعَةِ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(اسْتَبْشَعَ)</span> الشَّيْءَ عَدَّهُ بَشِعًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>